B6 case is a '70 Type 1 1600 DR SP, no bus mount there.
( B5 case is 68-69 Bus 1600 SR or '70 Bus 1600 DR )

Call Gene Berg for the SPG pattern flywheel tool.
It can be drilled in place with a hand drill and their reamer.
